### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### List all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

###

### Get user by ID (replace with a real UUID from the list response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_UUID
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

###

### Get user — not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

###

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

{
  "name": "Ketaki",
  "email": "ketaki@example.com"
}

###

### Create user — duplicate email (should return 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

{
  "name": "Duplicate",
  "email": "akshad@example.com"
}

###

### Update a user (replace UUID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_UUID
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: secret-key-123

{
  "name": "Akshad Jaiswal Updated",
  "email": "akshad.updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete a user (replace UUID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_UUID
X-API-Key: secret-key-123
